text: Aljaž Hočevar (born 20 August 1991) is a Slovenian former cyclist, who rode professionally between 2010 and 2014 for the team. ==Major results== ;2011 : 3rd Tour of Vojvodina II ;2013 : 1st Trofej Umag : 2nd Central European Tour Budapest GP : 5th Banja Luka Belgrade I ;2014 : 2nd Central European Tour Budapest GP : 6th Trofej Umag ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian male cyclists
